metadata.name: GW00 : Elana
metadata.description:
Silver Warrior Elana is one of the leaders of the elite unit and one of the most skilled weapons users..
Ilana joined the army after her city was attacked by invaders and received extensive training, which qualified her to fight fierce battles.

Video details: 1230 x 1080  ( 30 FPS )
10 seconds looping video

Collector will have the original 9000 x 5755 PNG file
